            <p><add hand="#barker">Sending a contribution for Texas</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>To <persName>Genl Austin</persName>, <persName>Col Wharton</persName> and <persName>Dr Archer</persName></p>

<p>Gentlemen</p>

<p>Feeling interested for the Cause of <placeName>Texas</placeName>, and being So Situated in life
that I cannot aid them personally I would beg Your acceptance of the
Within as a Small testimony of My good wishes for their Success, over the
blood thirsty Tyrant of the <persName>Mexican butchers</persName></p>

<p><persName>John Leadbetter Jr </persName>[Rubric]</p>

<p><placeName>Philada</placeName>. <date when="1836-05-02">May 2nd 1836</date></p>



        </div1>
